<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Verify your Aarogentix account</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
            background: #f1f5f9;
        }

        .wrapper {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 16px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb 0%, #1d4ed8 100%);
            padding: 40px 32px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: #fff;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        .header p {
            color: #bfdbfe;
            margin: 6px 0 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .body {
            padding: 40px 32px;
        }

        .body p {
            color: #374151;
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin: 0 0 16px;
        }

        .btn-wrap {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 32px 0;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #2563eb;
            color: #ffffff !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 14px 36px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 0.2px;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background: #1d4ed8;
        }

        .url-fallback {
            background: #f8fafc;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #64748b;
            word-break: break-all;
            margin-top: 24px;
        }

        .footer {
            background: #f8fafc;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            padding: 24px 32px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .footer p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #94a3b8;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Aarogentix</h1>
            <p>Healthcare Management System</p>
        </div>
        <div class="body">
            <p>Hi <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>
            <p>Welcome to Aarogentix! Please verify your email address to activate your account. This link expires in
                <strong>{{expiryHours}} hours</strong>.</p>
            <div class="btn-wrap">
                <a class="btn" href="{{verifyUrl}}">Verify Email Address</a>
            </div>
            <p>If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
            <div class="url-fallback">{{verifyUrl}}</div>
            <p style="margin-top:24px; color:#94a3b8; font-size:13px;">
                If you did not create an Aarogentix account, you can safely ignore this email.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>© {{year}} Aarogentix. All rights reserved.<br />This is an automated message — please do not reply.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>